properties.name: Dad Bod
properties.description:
This week we celebrate Fathers' Day early with a sort of softly round ride, a middle-age ride. It's a taking the kids to softball practice ride. It's a chain restaurant dinner out ride. It's a quick nine holes with the work buddies ride. It's a putting in 40+ hours at the J-O-B ride. So buy this ride a neck tie. Or make it a ceramic ashtray, even though it quit smoking ten years ago. This ride put on a few pounds after that and never quite lost them. The midriff is a bit doughy on this ride here. Maybe chip in for a NordicTrack for this ride. Or take this ride on a bike ride, perhaps?
